Remove Sudo Passcode (do not need to write sudo pass ever again) echo "$USER ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL" | sudo tee /etc/sudoers.d/$USER

Installing yay:sudo pacman -S --needed git base-devel && git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/yay.git && cd yay && makepkg -si

Installing bauh:yay -S bauh (an app store to manage aur and flatpak and appimage)

Installing flatpak:sudo pacman -S flatpak (reboot after)

Installing KDE Discover:sudo pacman -S plasma-discover plasma-discover-backend-flatpak

#Recommended flatpak might be slow or not install at first try.Install something like spotify: flatpak install flathub com.spotify.Client
via Terminal to fix it.
